================================================================================
REGULATORY COMPLIANCE NOTICE
================================================================================

This software is designed for use in regulated financial services environments
and implements controls aligned with:

- Financial Stability Board (FSB) AI guidance
- Bank for International Settlements (BIS) requirements
- Commodity Futures Trading Commission (CFTC) standards
- Federal Reserve and OCC model risk management frameworks

Users are responsible for ensuring their use complies with applicable
regulatory requirements in their jurisdiction.

